Package cs3500.easyanimator.model

Interface IReadOnlyModel

All Superinterfaces:
IAnimationModel
All Known Implementing Classes:
ReadOnlyModelImpl
public interface IReadOnlyModel
extends IAnimationModel
A read-only version of the model. Should not support any methods that manipulate data. Throws an UnsupportedOperationException for unsupported method calls that may cause manipulation of data.
